messages.message: We do expect Converse to understand many tables, but definitely not every table. I can see though that for this document for this table the model performs especially poor. cc @Rafal @vineeth will be a good document to add to the benchmarking dataset.

We are working on better support for tables. @Lalit had much better results on his dataset when introducing features from Form Recognizer
@Lalit can you please add it to your test dataset?
I'll perform more analysis and surely add this to the benchmark dataset.
